channel.description:
[ul]Welcome to Project Destiny.
Project Destiny 317, Project Destiny is a newly opened server, we currently have 15 Bosses and looking forward to add some more. We're actively looking for staff, and we're handpicking them ourselves. We have Dicing, Flower Games and such our interface is better looking. We have just opened our client page, Homepage And Forums, Please visit and get a feedback of our server.
